00:19:17.980 --> 00:19:19.540
few words on the interaction
design here.

00:19:19.540 --> 00:19:23.820
So the way the app currently
works, if you single tap on an

00:19:23.820 --> 00:19:27.230
item in the list, it then pops
up an old-style quick action

00:19:27.230 --> 00:19:30.330
bar, which lets you do things
